"v.合并；混合 【英】 v.合并(unite; combine)；混合(to combine in an amalgam) 【考】 反义词： separate(分离); isolate(隔离) 【记】 来自单词amalgam(合 金, 混合物) 【例】 Our school will amalgamate with another school. v. 合并 = unite = combine; 混合 = admix = interfuse 【例】That school will amalgamate with another school 那所学校将和另一所学校合并. 【记】来自单词amalgam(n 汞合金, 混合物) 【反】separate(v 分离); isolate(v 隔离); disintegrate(vt 使分解) 【记】amalgam + ate 动词 amalgamate (v.)  1650s, back-formation from amalgamation, or from adjective amalgamate (1640s) from amalgam. Originally in metallurgy; figurative sense of ""to unite"" (races, etc.) is attested from 1802. Related: Amalgamated; amalgamating. Earlier verb was amalgamen (1540s)."
